This directory contains a font vendored unmodified for use by gimoji-web.

JetBrains Mono Regular
  Source: https://github.com/JetBrains/JetBrainsMono
  Version: 2.304
  License: Apache-2.0 — https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0

Emoji glyphs are rendered as DOM overlay using the browser's system emoji
font stack (Apple Color Emoji / Segoe UI Emoji / Noto Color Emoji), so no
emoji font is bundled.
